  <name>Archi</name>
  <summary>Open source ArchiMate modeling tool</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Archi is an open source modeling tool for creating ArchiMate models and sketches.
      ArchiMate® is an open and independent modeling language for Enterprise Architecture
      that is supported by different tool vendors and consulting firms.
    </p>
    <p>
      Key features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Full support for ArchiMate 3.2 specification</li>
      <li>Easy to use visual modeling with drag and drop</li>
      <li>Multiple views and viewpoints</li>
      <li>Model relationship management</li>
      <li>Import/Export to various formats</li>
      <li>Collaboration features with coArchi plugin</li>
      <li>HTML report generation</li>
      <li>Cross-platform support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
  <launchable type="desktop-id">com.archimatetool.Archi.desktop</launchable>
  
